PN,37701
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1773668258
OL,3,CDerbyshire pottery firm Denby to
OL,4,Cappoint administrators
OL,6,FThe historic Derbyshire pottery firm
OL,7,FDenby has confirmed plans to appoint
OL,8,Fadministrators saying that it has been
OL,9,Fstruggling with rising energy prices.
OL,11,FThe ceramics company, which dates back
OL,12,Fmore than 200 years to the early
OL,13,F1800s, has said it is a precautionary
OL,14,Fmeasure to provide a "period of
OL,15,Fstability".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1773668258
OL,3,CDerbyshire pottery firm Denby to
OL,4,Cappoint administrators
OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "While Denby has
OL,7,Fexplored a range of options, it has
OL,8,Fnot yet been able to secure a
OL,9,Fstrategic investment partner aligned
OL,10,Fwith the long-term vision and values
OL,11,Fof its historic British brands much
OL,12,Floved by their large global fan base.
OL,13,FThe search for a suitable partner will
OL,14,Fcontinue whether for the Denby Group
OL,15,Fas a whole or for the brands
OL,16,Findividually.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1773668258
OL,3,CDerbyshire pottery firm Denby to
OL,4,Cappoint administrators
OL,6,F"As a precautionary measure, and to
OL,7,Fprovide a period of stability while
OL,8,Fthese options continue to be assessed,
OL,9,Fthe Denby group of companies in the UK
OL,10,Fhas filed a notice of intention to
OL,11,Fappoint administrators. This step
OL,12,Foffers short-term protection to allow
OL,13,Fthe business to explore potential
OL,14,Ffunding and restructuring solutions in
OL,15,Fan orderly manner."
OL,17,FThe GMB union, which represents
OL,18,Fworkers at Denby Pottery Group, says
OL,19,Fit is supporting members.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1773668258
OL,3,CDerbyshire pottery firm Denby to
OL,4,Cappoint administrators
OL,6,FCraig Thomson, GMB Organiser, said:
OL,7,F"Denby pottery is a British icon,
OL,8,Fproducing some of the world's finest
OL,9,Fceramics.
OL,11,F"This is a worrying time for workers
OL,12,Facross Denby. We are working closely
OL,13,Fwith our members and reps on site.
OL,15,F"Britain's ceramics industry is the
OL,16,Fenvy of the world. We must now see
OL,17,Furgent government action on energy
OL,18,Fprices to support the sector through
OL,19,Fthis time of turbulence".
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU{D@XO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1773668258
OL,3,CDerbyshire pottery firm Denby to
OL,4,Cappoint administrators
OL,6,FIn the House of Commons earlier this
OL,7,Fweek the Prime Minister said the
OL,8,FGovernment was in talks with the
OL,9,Fceramics industry over potentially
OL,10,Fextending the supercharger scheme
OL,11,Fwhich aims to reduce costs for energy
OL,12,Fintensive industries.
OL,14,FLinsey Farnsworth, Labour MP for Amber
OL,15,FValley, said her focus was on "trying
OL,16,Fto ensure the stability of this vital
OL,17,Flocal employer and protecting the
OL,18,Flivelihoods of its workforce".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1773668258
OL,3,CDerbyshire pottery firm Denby to
OL,4,Cappoint administrators
OL,6,F"I have already held an urgent meeting
OL,7,Fwith Denby's leadership to discuss the
OL,8,Fcurrent situation and determine how I
OL,9,Fcan best support through this
OL,10,Fprocess," she said.
OL,12,F"I have also been in contact with GMB
OL,13,Funion representatives to ensure that
OL,14,Fthe voices of the employees are heard
OL,15,Fduring this period of uncertainty.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1773668258
OL,3,CDerbyshire pottery firm Denby to
OL,4,Cappoint administrators
OL,6,F"Having previously raised the specific
OL,7,Fpressures facing the ceramics sector,
OL,8,Fparticularly industrial energy costs,
OL,9,Fboth in Parliament and directly with
OL,10,Fministers, I will continue to advocate
OL,11,Ffor the support Denby needs at a
OL,12,Fministerial level.
OL,14,F"I am actively engaged with the
OL,15,FTreasury and the Department of
OL,16,FBusiness and Trade. Denby remains a
OL,17,Fworld-class, viable manufacturer that
OL,18,Fcontinues to trade and meet demand.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1773668258
OL,3,CDerbyshire pottery firm Denby to
OL,4,Cappoint administrators
OL,6,F"I am acting as a direct link between
OL,7,Fthe company and the Department for
OL,8,FBusiness and Trade to ensure every
OL,9,Fpossible avenue is explored to secure
OL,10,Fa positive outcome for Amber Valley."
